title: UnitedHealth posts modest earnings beat, soft revenue guidance as insurer plots turnaround
summary: UnitedHealth expects 2026 revenue to come in greater than $439 billion, which is a 2% year-over-year decline that reflects "right-sizing across the enterprise."

title: US health insurer shares fall on proposal to cut rise in Medicare payments
summary: UnitedHealth and Humana drop more than 10% after hours on Monday on news of Trump administration’s plan
